{"tid":989871,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"日本網民希望立方獸(3D龍)能夠在平成最後再次出現在寵物小精靈動畫中","createTime":"2019-01-21T07:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-25T00:08:26.000Z","uid":100680,"like":115,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"77c45b5bf8f0f934421fafc60840183f361a5d71","tid":989871,"uid":100680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:43:30.000Z","msg":"轉自推特 @Cha_ros 所畫的漫畫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/gUNeb8jTwb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgUNeb8jTwb&d=DzQ%2BdqR9z8afoqiyVUfjdXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=4236bd66\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/gUNeb8jTwb</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dw8zTxXVsAIgXGF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDw8zTxXVsAIgXGF.jpg&h=a21ce342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「立方獸」一聽到這個名字，<br />\n大家會想起20年前那件事吧<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n1997年12月16日播出的寵物小精靈動畫，<br />\n由於過度使用光亮的演出，<br />\n造成700多人頭痛或嘔吐。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n這個事件被稱為「寵物小精靈休克症」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dw8zTxVUUAAYLGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDw8zTxVUUAAYLGA.jpg&h=fed57291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於這件事動畫被停播4個月...也成為以後任何動畫<br />\n「請保持室內明亮、不要太靠近電視機」<br />\n這個電視節目片頭警語誕生的契機。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n該集來賓的立方獸被永久在動畫封殺&hellip;<br />\n這20年來沒再出現在電視上過。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n但是這實際上是一件非常奇怪的事<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n好像是把立方獸龍當成元兇一樣<br />\n在那次動畫中，立方獸只不過是讓小智他們坐上去而已啊<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n要說到此事件受災的罪魁祸首<br />\n應當是比卡超向飛彈發出電擊的那一幕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dw8zTxYU8AAvkjy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDw8zTxYU8AAvkjy.jpg&h=d66ba45d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比卡超...不，真要追究起來<br />\n這本來是動畫製作人員的鍋<br />\n但是被判永久入獄的卻是立方獸...<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n人工寶可夢就此葬送在那些所謂＂大人＂的手裡。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n還不僅是這樣...<br />\n連立方獸進化型的立方獸2跟立方獸Z<br />\n他們至今也從未在動畫登場過<br />\n<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n當時6歲的我如今也已經是大人了。<br />\n深知20年是歷經了多長的歲月。<br />\n                                                         <br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/Dw8zTxYUUAACC3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDw8zTxYUUAACC3r.jpg&h=6b60142e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現在已經習慣遠離電視觀看。<br />\n應該已經沒有理由不讓立方獸在動畫出現才對。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n所以我希望立方獸能在動畫上出現。<br />\n希望能讓許多人知道立方獸並非是壞蛋。<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n希望讓立方獸...重見光明<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n希望讓3D龍一族...能夠在平成最後　挽回名聲<br />\n                                                                                <br />\n                                                                                <br />\n當年宛如恐怖攻擊般的「立方獸事件」<br />\n幫真正罪魁祸首比卡超和動畫制作人員背鍋，坐了這麼多年的冤牢<br />\n也該是時候放立方獸出獄了吧？"},{"pid":"d723154188b51b9a477dbed563f39cbc05a6efb1","tid":989871,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd9125d2d6e49d45e76cc66b37622eaa0148b85","tid":989871,"uid":199668,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:16:37.000Z","msg":"立方獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d56450d7c69485e0c83fbd5133f3e11abe2bbe","tid":989871,"uid":4780,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:43:05.000Z","msg":"請還立方獸一個公道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f5016ddd63cde6362c74d2fba6997dcb00043b","tid":989871,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":216,"score":-216,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"叫開多邊獸<br />\n立方獸係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c58c9af32ac61e9a0ea24162a988f4c3d6f93ce","tid":989871,"uid":37157,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"90f5016ddd63cde6362c74d2fba6997dcb00043b","tid":989871,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":216,"score":-216,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"叫開多邊獸<br />\n立方獸係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8886e424086d180137c74057187c56efbe493f24","tid":989871,"uid":51388,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"90f5016ddd63cde6362c74d2fba6997dcb00043b","tid":989871,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":216,"score":-216,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"叫開多邊獸<br />\n立方獸係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0